873
01:22:54,700 --> 01:22:57,000
Hummm... la maladie d'amour.

874
01:22:59,700 --> 01:23:00,600
Et toi ?

875
01:23:02,600 --> 01:23:03,600
Hé !

876
01:23:05,200 --> 01:23:06,400
Une maladie mortelle.

877
01:23:08,300 --> 01:23:09,200
Hein ?

878
01:23:59,900 --> 01:24:03,000
Ça ne sera pas facile de voir
